	Package: qrencode
	Description: Utility to generate pngs from QR Codes
	
	Depends: %N-shlibs (= %v-%r), libpng16-shlibs
	
	Files: bin share
	
	DocFiles: ChangeLog COPYING NEWS README TODO
<<
